# Title: Service Startup Type Change Via Wmic.EXE
# Author: Swachchhanda Shrawan Poudel (Nextron Systems)
# Date: 2026-04-27
# Level: medium
# Description: Detects changes to service startup type to 'disabled' or 'manual' using the WMIC command-line utility.
# MITRE Tactic: Execution
# Tags: attack.execution, attack.defense-impairment, attack.t1047, attack.t1685
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/process_creation/proc_creation_win_wmic_service_startup_change.yml
# False Positives:
#   - Legitimate administrative changes to service startup types using WMIC, investigate accordingly.

CommandLine IN ("*Manual*", "*Disabled*") CommandLine="* service *" CommandLine="*ChangeStartMode*" Image="*\\WMIC.exe" OR OriginalFileName="wmic.exe"